Package com.github.ponkin.bloom

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Filter
    Common filter interface.
    FilterBuilder<T extends Filter>
    Common builder interface for all filters
    HashFunction
    Common functional interface for all hashing strategies.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BloomFilter
    Classic bloom filter implementation To calculate hash by default Murmur3 hash is used (128 bit) but this can be changed in builder.
    BloomFilter.Builder
    Builder for BloomFilter
    CuckooFilter
    Cuckoo filter implementation.
    CuckooFilter.Builder
    Builder for CuckooFilter
    Hashers
    HashFunctions implementations
    ScalableBloomFilter
    Scalable bloom filter implementation http://gsd.di.uminho.pt/members/cbm/ps/dbloom.pdf Scalable Bloom Filters are useful for cases where the size of the data set isn't known a priori and memory constraints aren't of particular concern.
    StableBloomFilter
    StableBloomFilter implements a Stable Bloom Filter as described by Deng and Rafiei in Approximately Detecting Duplicates for Streaming Data using Stable Bloom Filters: http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~drafiei/papers/DupDet06Sigmod.pdf A Stable Bloom Filter (SBF) continuously evicts stale information so that it has room for more recent elements.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncompatibleMergeException
    Special Exception, thrown when two incompatible filters are merged.
